{"all_questions_require_answer":true,"name":"Weis - 8 O'Clock Coffee - Try Our New Great Tastes - Cycle 8","qc_comments":"","objective":"CPG Brand Client","id":68728,"instructions":"Go to the store at the ADDRESS listed above.  

Locate the coffee section in the Grocery department to find the 8 O'Clock Coffee product.

Look for an approximate 5” X 7” advertising sign for 8 O'Clock Coffee-Try Our New Great Tastes (see product details below). The sign may be  in front of the product attached to the shelf or near the product. 

Take (1) picture of the sign making sure to capture about 2 feet of the space surrounding the product & sign. If no sign is present, a picture of the 8 O'Clock Coffee product is needed. If the product is not carried in the store, take a photo of the coffee section where the item and sign would be. Photos must be clear & easily viewable. 
"}

{"all_questions_require_answer":true,"name":"Wakefern - Pedigree - Real Meat is the #1 Ingredient - Cycle 8","qc_comments":"","objective":"CPG Brand Client","id":68731,"instructions":"Go to the store at the ADDRESS listed above.  

Locate the dog food section in the Grocery department to find the Pedigree-Real Meat is the #1 Ingredient product.

Look for an approximate 5” X 7” advertising sign for Pedigree-Real Meat is the #1 Ingredient  (see product details below). The sign may be  in front of the product attached to the shelf or near the product. 

Take (1) picture of the sign making sure to capture about 2 feet of the space surrounding the product & sign. If no sign is present, a picture of the Pedigree product is needed. If the product is not carried in the store, take a photo of the dog food section where the item and sign would be. Photos must be clear & easily viewable. 

"}

Locate the coffee section in the Grocery department to find the 8 O'Clock Coffee product.

Look for an approximate 5” X 7” advertising sign for 8 O'Clock Coffee-Try Me  (see product details below). The sign may be  in front of the product attached to the shelf or near the product. 

Take (1) picture of the sign making sure to capture about 2 feet of the space surrounding the product & sign. If no sign is present, a picture of the 8 O'Clock Coffee product is needed. If the product is not carried in the store, take a photo of the coffee section where the item and sign would be. Photos must be clear & easily viewable. 

"}
